@startuml Sequence_UC01
title UC-01: Login dan Logout

actor "Pengguna" as User
participant "Halaman Login\n(login.blade.php)" as View
participant "LoginController\n/ Livewire Auth" as Auth
participant "User Model" as UserModel
database "Database" as DB

== Login ==
User -> View: Membuka halaman /login
View --> User: Menampilkan form login

User -> View: Mengisi email & password\nlalu submit
View -> Auth: attempt(email, password)
Auth -> UserModel: where('email')->first()
UserModel -> DB: SELECT users WHERE email = ?
DB --> UserModel: User record
UserModel --> Auth: User instance

alt Email tidak ditemukan / password salah
  Auth --> View: Kembalikan error 'auth.failed'
  View --> User: Tampilkan pesan "Email atau password salah"
else Login berhasil
  Auth --> View: Redirect ke /dashboard
  View --> User: Tampilkan halaman dashboard
end

== Logout ==
User -> View: Menekan tombol Logout
View -> Auth: logout()
Auth -> DB: Invalidate session
Auth --> View: Redirect ke /login
View --> User: Tampilkan halaman login

@enduml
